---
title: Umami Ginger Meatball Bar One recipe—endless ways to enjoy!
description: Hard to find one option that pleases everyone? Introducing our chef-curated “perfect plates,” where everyone can build their own bowl. This one stars gingery beef meatballs, fluffy rice, tender roasted carrots, and a lineup of tantalizing toppers—tangy cucumber salad, umami ponzu sauce, Sriracha mayo, cilantro, and crispy fried onions.

